message.text:
BREAKING: Manila City Mayor Francisco “Isko Moreno” Domagoso suspends classes in COLLEGE (including Graduate Schools) only in both public and private schools due to a nationwide transport strike tomorrow, September 30.

However, classes from pre-school to senior high school will continue.

#AlertoManileno #WalangPasok

message.text:
WALANG PASOK: Based on the recommendation of Manila DRRM Office, AFTERNOON classes in ALL LEVELS in public and private schools are suspended on Monday, March 3, 2025.

According to the weather forecast by MDRRMO, Manila’s heat index this morning will range from 36-38°C, with peak heat index of 42°C to be felt around 2:00PM today.

#WalangPasok
